{"title":"Šampoonid","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Oak Shampoo For Men 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA modern approach to the world of men – primal and earthy components create a shampoo with a light, modern and delicate nature! A natural shampoo for everyday use. The shampoo with a fine lather and minimal composition contains a powerful oak root extract that soothes irritated scalp and stimulates hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 – 25 degrees. Protect from direct sunlight during storage. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Methyl Oleoyl Taurate, Lauryl Glucoside, Coco-Glucoside, Parfum, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Citric Acid, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Panthenol, Pentylene Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,88%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927684231495,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-oak-shampoo-for-men-250ml-302851.png?v=1739897400"},{"product_id":"solid-oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Solid Oak Shampoo For Men 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003ch6\u003e\n\u003cimg height=\"100\" width=\"93\" alt=\"pure beauty global awars 2022 winner\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/908145_pbga_winner_2022-280x300.png\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12056\"\u003e \u003cimg height=\"100\" width=\"87\" alt=\"pure beauty global awars 2022 highly commended\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/908142_pbga_highly_commended_2022-261x300.png\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12051\"\u003e\n\u003c\/h6\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA modern approach to the world of men – primal and earthy components create a shampoo with a light, modern and delicate nature! The richly-foaming, deep-cleaning solid shampoo ensures clean and healthy hair. The shampoo with a rich foam and minimal composition contains powerful oak root extract and cocoa butter, which together soothe irritated scalp and stimulate hair growth. The dynamic formula deep-cleans and facilitates styling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak extract\u003c\/span\u003e has natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 – 25 degrees. Protect from direct sunlight during storage. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Quercus Robur (Oak) Extract, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96,6%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927694061895,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-solid-oak-shampoo-for-men-58g-324609.png?v=1739897402"},{"product_id":"solid-linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract","title":"Magrada Volumizing Solid Shampoo With Linden Flower Extract 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle on your hair, and on the environment. The solid shampoo concentrate will last longer, while the packaging is made of recycled aluminium.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe richly foaming shampoo protects and conditions, softening and moisturising the scalp as well as the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract stimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is ideal for women, men, as well as children for daily use, and is also suitable for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe Nordic birch extract\u003c\/span\u003e, cocoa butter and dried herb inflorescences create a powerful trio which not only cleans, but also makes the hair livelier and fuller, not to mention the honey-sweet scent adding sugary notes to your day.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDried linden flowers\u003c\/span\u003e have an antioxidative and anti-inflammatory effect on The skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids which help to improve The protective function of The skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to The hair and improves The structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract*, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower, Glycerin, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96,5%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927702810951,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-volumizing-solid-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-58g-5420286.png?v=1763665704"},{"product_id":"rhubarb-shampoo-with-aloe-extract-250-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/auhinnad-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2022\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour hair is ready for invigoration. Indulge it with spring-like freshness, gloss, and shine!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe juicy rhubarb-enriched shampoo is designed for intensive enlivening of dry and damaged hair. The extra moisturising aloe extract with Pro-Vitamin B5 restores, nurtures, and reinforces the damaged hair structure. The vitamin treatment that your hair needs.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Citric Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract*, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Parfum, Panthenol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,57%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulfate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e| alcohol-free |\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927708479815,"sku":"","price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-250ml-1916309.png?v=1763665704"},{"product_id":"clarifying-solid-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract","title":"Magrada Clarifying Solid Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAn eco-friendly alternative to classical shampoos. Thanks to its concentrated formula, the solid shampoo will last longer, and its packaging is made of recycled aluminium.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo enriched with rhubarb extract strengthens hair, helps remove flaking skin from the scalp, prevents scalp irritation, and gives the hair an extraordinary shine. The shampoo also helps to deep-clean the hair and scalp from oils, sweat, and product residue. This results in lovely clean hair, scented with juicy red rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is ideal for women, men, and children for daily use and is also suitable for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties and it helps sooth a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids, which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927718834503,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-clarifying-solid-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-58g-486824.png?v=1739897405"},{"product_id":"linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Shampoo With Linden Flower Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/1-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2019\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/2-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"iluteemant proff soovitab\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTake the summer with you – the linden flower shampoo with birch extract is a powerful Nordic elixir which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The sweet scent of the shampoo will take you back to warm summer memories in a blink, bringing a smile to your face even on a bitterly cold winter morning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe invigorating shampoo will make your hair less frizzy, nurturing and moisturising the structure of the hair and giving it a beautiful gloss and shine. The organic plant extracts support hair growth and improve the elasticity of the hair. The hair is soft, light, flowing after washing!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for daily use for the entire family, including for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic Nordic birch extract\u003c\/span\u003e stimulates circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters*, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Glycerin, Alcohol, Panthenol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: \u003cspan\u003e97,44%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927725683015,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-250ml-8194248.png?v=1763665704"},{"product_id":"reise-rice-extract-gentle-cleansing-shampoo-350ml","title":"REISE Rice Extract Gentle Cleansing Shampoo 350ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAmino Acid based surfactants and Rice Bran Extract deliver mild cleaning and hydrating.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eProvides fullness and plush softness with natural, fluid movement.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eRice Bran Extract is enriched with multiple vitamins and protein. Combining with the natural derived Amino Acid based surfactants, this product is mild and non-irritating to every types of skin, and nourishes the hair. Special adding Nettle Root Extract to balance sebum production. With a hint of lemon balm and lemon aroma. Alcohol free, animal ingredients free. Leaving your scalp fresh and breathable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eBio-based packaging made from rice bran. Rice bran is a byproduct of the conversion from brown rice to white rice. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eEvery rice bran bottle can reduce 46% plastic usage, 36% energy usage and 38% carbon dioxide emission.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Pour on wet hand and fully massage lather into hair and scalp, then rinse off.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Camellia Sinensis Seed Extract, Sodium Lauroyl Glutamate, Cocoamidopropyl Betaine, Decyl Glucoside, Sea Salt Extract, Camella Oleifera Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Corn Gluten Amino Acids, Hydrolyzed Rice Protein, Irakusa Ne Ekisu Extract, Coconut Oil, Wheat Germ Oil, Carrageenan, Sucrose Cocoate, Oryza Sativa Bran Extract, Nicotinic Acid, Melissa Officinalis Leaf Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Citric Acid, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil *, Chlorhexidine Digluconate, Sodium Anisate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal ingredients free | Silicone-free | Alcohol-free | No SLS\/SLES | No Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade In Taiwan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Reise","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49274437894471,"sku":"","price":22.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/reise-rice-extract-gentle-cleansing-shampoo-350ml-163826.jpg?v=1739897347"},{"product_id":"bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml","title":"BEE IT Nourishing Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing shampoo for damaged hair and scalp. It cleanses with care, maintaining the original structure of the hair with an energetic action. The soft creamy texture creates a light lather with extra ordinary effectiveness for soft and vital hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to wet scalp and hair, massaging gently. Rinse gently, inhaling and exhaling slowly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Xanthan gum, Glycerin, Disodium cocoamphodiacetate, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Citric acid, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Panthenol, Argania spinosa kernel oil, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Mel\/Honey*, Coumarin, Limonene, Dehydroacetic acid, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, CI 19140 [Yellow 5].\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354464756039,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml-159598.jpg?v=1739897346"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Blue for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354588979527,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml-687213.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354641178951,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml-813819.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF 2-in-1 Shampoo \u0026 Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e2-in-1 kids Shampoo \u0026amp; Conditioner for all hairtypes (long, short, thick or curly). The shampoo cleanses your hair while the anti-tangle formula ensures that the hair is soft and easy to comb through. Softens and detangles hair and hydrates with sunflower- and linseed oil. For all kids. Without SLES or microplastics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMild, fruity scent developed for and by children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eTake a coin-sized amount of Naif 2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner and massage into wet hair. Leave it in for a bit, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Inulin, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445993644359,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-851648.png?v=1739897337"},{"product_id":"naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Nourishing Shampoo for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA nourishing shampoo developed specifically to tame those wild kids' hairs. The shampoo cleanses and softens the hair to make it easier to comb through. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaif's kids shampoo contains a special anti-tangle formula and is packed with a selection of natural ingredients, like cottonseed extract and hydrolyzed wheat protein. Cares for both hair and scalp, without microplastics, silicones and SLES. So, it’s mild for the eyes too.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a coin-sized amount of shampoo and massage into wet hair, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446040371527,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml-208574.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"nurme-lemongrass-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","title":"NURME Lemongrass Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme’s natural shampoos are based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. This shampoo contains only plant based ingredients. It’s gentle on your hair and the environment. The product is packaged in a recyclable plastic packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLemongrass shampoo is 100% natural, adds a beautiful shine and is great for hair that grease easily, as it regulates perspiration and keeps hair cleaner for longer.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe shampoo contains lemongrass essential oil, one of the most popular oils in Nurme’s range. Hair strengthening\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eProVitamin B5\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with lemongrass hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Panthenol (Provitamin B5), Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Leaf Oil, Citral*, Geraniol*. *Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553830707527,"sku":"","price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lemongrass-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250ml-532679.webp?v=1739897237"},{"product_id":"nurme-lemongrass-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml-copy","title":"NURME Rosemary Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250 ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme’s natural shampoos are based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. The shampoo contains only plant-based ingredients. It is gentle for your hair and for the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis natural rosemary shampoo contains gentle surfactants that create a creamy lather and are mild on the skin. The hair-strengthening ProVitamin B5 helps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNatural rosemary shampoo helps to relieve dry scalp problems and is rated by users as one of the best hair cleansers to fight dandruff. Stress, the changing seasons and a weakened immune system are just a few of the factors that can cause white patches of dandruff to cover the scalp.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRosemary soothes itchy scalps and contains anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial components, so in milder cases, the right choice of shampoo may be all you need to get rid of dandruff.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with rosemary hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside**, Sodium Coco-Sulfate**, Sodium Chloride**, Panthenol (ProVitamin B5), Citric Acid**, Glyceryl Oleate**, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein**, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Oil**, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate**, Limonene*. *Occures naturally in essential oils. **Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553831199047,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-rosemary-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250-ml-151169.jpg?v=1739897251"},{"product_id":"nurme-lavender-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","title":"NURME Lavender Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme’s natural shampoos are based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. The shampoo contains only plant-based ingredients. It is gentle for your hair and for the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNurme Lavender Shampoo helps to repair damaged hair and split ends while promoting hair growth. In addition, the enchanting scent of lavender has a soothing effect.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo contains gentle surfactants that create a creamy lather and are mild on the skin. The hair-strengthening ProVitamin B5 helps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLavender essential oil is richly nourishing, moisturizes the scalp and hair, helps prevent hair loss, and improves scalp circulation, thereby promoting hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with lavender hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside**, Sodium Coco-Sulfate**, Sodium Chloride**, Panthenol (ProVitamin B5), Citric Acid**, Glyceryl Oleate**, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein**, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate**, Linalool*. *Occures naturally in essential oils. **Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553853612359,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lavender-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250ml-378356.jpg?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"nurme-ylang-ylang-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","title":"NURME Ylang-Ylang Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme organic shampoo is based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. The shampoo contains only plant-based ingredients. It is gentle for your hair and for the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYlang-Ylang shampoo helps to reduce hair loss and balance dry scalp. Ylang-ylang essential oil is known as a good moisturizer and it also promotes hair regrowth. Ylang-ylang has a sweet floral scent and reminds you those warm summer days.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo contains gentle surfactants that create a creamy lather and are mild on the skin. The hair-strengthening ProVitamin B5 helps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with ylang-ylang hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Panthenol (Provitamin B5), Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Cananga Odorata (Ylang Ylang) Flower Oil, Linalool*.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e*Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553854824775,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-ylang-ylang-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250ml-446160.jpg?v=1739897237"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-shampoo-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic shampoo, specially designed to cleanse, repair and moisturise damaged hair and sensitive scalps gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), black oats (moisturising), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to wet hair. Massage gently into hair and on scalp. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Xanthan Gum*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Hydrolyzed Wheat Gluten*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Lecithin*, Avena Strigosa Seed Extract*, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (68,1%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50900996653383,"sku":null,"price":30.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-shampoo-250ml-599294.webp?v=1739897169"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml","title":"NURME Mild Baby Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel is a gentle cleanser that is particularly suitable for sensitive skin and can be used to wash the baby from their very first bath. The shampoo\/shower gel contains natural wheat protein and moisturizes the skin even during dry winter months. Organic and plant-based ingredients work like magic, nourishing the skin and cleansing the child from head to tiny toes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBaby skin is soft and delicate. It is more sensitive than adult skin and can easily become dry, painful, and flaky.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eIt is essential to use specially formulated products for infants to protect their delicate skin from damage.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eNurme Baby Range products, including the Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, help care for a baby’s delicate skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOf course, this cleansing product can also be used by all other family members, especially those with sensitive skin!\u003cspan\u003e Nurme Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, with its pure composition, is very gentle on the skin while being effective.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of shampoo\/shower gel to a washcloth or palm and gently massage the baby’s head and body. Rinse with water afterward. If the product gets into the eyes, rinse thoroughly with water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua*, Coco-Glucoside*, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Chloride*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915990241607,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml-327281.webp?v=1739897183"},{"product_id":"madara-nourish-and-repair-shampoo-250ml","title":"MÁDARA Nourish and Repair shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eDeeply nourish and cleanse the hair with this rich and silky shampoo.  Formulated with Northern Nettle and Quince, It gently cleanses and repairs dry, damaged hair. Fights fatigue and helps to prevent breakage and split ends. Plus, this shampoo is packaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle to reduce the volume of new plastic bottles made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003eGently massage into wet hair. Lather and rinse with water. For best results, use in combination with MÁDARA Nourish and Repair Conditioner.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Coco-glucoside, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Betaine, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Chloride, Citric acid, Aroma, Benzyl Alcohol, Brassica Alcohol, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Fruit Extract, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917134696775,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-nourish-and-repair-shampoo-250ml-100093.jpg?v=1739897193"},{"product_id":"madara-colour-and-shine-shampoo-250ml","title":"MÁDARA Colour and Shine shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGently cleanse and protect treated and coloured hair with this colour enhancing shampoo, enriched with Northern Linseed, Horse Chestnut and Plantain. After use, hair becomes softer to the touch and reflects luminous light. Plus, this shampoo is packaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle to reduce the volume of new plastic bottles made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently massage into wet hair. Lather and rinse with water. For best results, use in combination with MÁDARA Colour and Shine Conditioner.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Coco-glucoside, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Lactic Acid, Aroma, Benzyl Alcohol, Plantago Major (Plantain) Leaf Extract, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Extract, Brassica Alcohol, Citric acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917150163271,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-colour-and-shine-shampoo-250ml-156178.jpg?v=1739897178"},{"product_id":"madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-shampoo-250ml","title":"MÁDARA Gloss and Vibrancy shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGently cleanse and protect the hair with this shine–enhancing and volume-boosting shampoo. Formulated with Northern Birch and Cranberry, it ensures stronger, silkier and shinier hair. Plus, this shampoo is packaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle to reduce the volume of new plastic bottles made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently massage into wet hair. Lather and rinse with water. For best results, use in combination with MÁDARA Gloss And Vibrancy Conditioner.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Coco-glucoside, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Citric acid, Sodium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Aroma, Behenyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract, Brassica Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917168873799,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-shampoo-250ml-798928.jpg?v=1739897192"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-verbena-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Verbena 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Verbena shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. The citrus extracts in Verbena ensure that your locks get a beautiful shine. In addition, this shampoo bar contains Coconut Butter, Macadamia Nut Oil and Olive Oil, ingredients that nourish and care for every hair type.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Verbena shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Verbena is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Our packaging is 100% plastic-free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Mentha Piperita Leaf Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Pinus Sylvestris Bud, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Limonene, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, Linalool, CI 12490, CI 51319.\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938645709127,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-verbena-60g-542685.jpg?v=1739897163"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-tea-tree-lemon-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Tea Tree \u0026 Lemon 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Tea Tree \u0026amp; Lemon shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. This shampoo bar contains natural Coconut Butter, Macadamia Nut Oil and Olive Oil, which forms a good basis for healthy, hydrated and shiny hair. The Tea Tree Oil that has been added has a degreasing and cleansing effect and works well against skin irritations. This makes it fantastic for your scalp and stimulates the strength of your hair roots!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Tea Tree \u0026amp; Lemon shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Tea Tree \u0026amp; Lemon is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tee) Leaf Oil, Limonene, Linalool, Citral, Geraniol, CI 42051, CI 19140\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938672447815,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-tea-tree-lemon-60g-472941.jpg?v=1739897153"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-chamomile-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Chamomile 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the chamomile shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. However, this shampoo bar is particularly suitable for blonde hair and is a sustainable alternative to silver shampoo. Chamomile is also used to lighten blond hair, and highly concentrated chamomile is even used to bleach hair. The chamomile extracts in this Chamomile shampoo bar give your hair a natural shine and make it lighter. With your blonde locks you can leave the house radiant again!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Chamomile shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Chamomile is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita Flower, Phenoxyethanol, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Linalool, Coumarin, Geraniol, CI 19140\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938681393479,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-chamomile-60g-262939.jpg?v=1739897154"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-grapefruit-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Grapefruit 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Grapefruit shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. This shampoo bar contains Shea butter, Macadamia nut oil, Grape seed oil and Bitter Orange extract. These oils and extracts nourish the hair and strengthen the rejuvenating powers of your hair. In addition, the citrusy aromas of the Grapefruit Shampoo bar help to stimulate your senses so that you can face the day full of energy! \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Grapefruit shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Grapefruit is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape ) Seed Oil, Citrus Aurantium Amara Peel Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Benzyl Benzoate, Limonene, CI 19140, CI 15985\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938693681479,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-grapefruit-60g-652534.jpg?v=1739897163"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-eucalyptus-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Eucalyptus 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the eucalyptus shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. However, this shampoo bar is particularly suitable for oily hair. Eucalyptus has a degreasing effect, which means that it absorbs grease on your hair and roots. The shampoo bar is enriched with pure eucalyptus oil, which is not only good for your hair, inhaling it in the shower is also very good for your respiratory tract. With this Eucalyptus shampoo bar you not only wash your hair gently, you also have to wash your hair less often because your hair becomes greasy less quickly!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Eucalyptus shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Eucalyptus is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Eucalyptus Alba Leaf Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Equisetum Arvense Leaf, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Eugenol, CI 74260, CI 42051, CI 19140\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938697646407,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-eucalyptus-60g-519891.jpg?v=1739897153"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-pine-cone-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Pine Cone 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Pinecone shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. This wintery scent opens your airways in the shower and nourishes your hair. All shampoo bars that are suitable for all hair types contain a combination of different natural products such as Coconut butter, Macadamia nut oil and Olive oil. The delicious pine cone extracts complete your winter look with fresh and well-groomed hair. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Pine Cone shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Pine Cone is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Pinus Sylvestris Bud Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Pinus Sylvestris Bud, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Benzyl Benzoate, Coumarin, Limonene, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol, Amyl Cinnamal, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938705281351,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-pine-cone-60g-109790.jpg?v=1739897165"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-lavender-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Lavender 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the lavender shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. However, this shampoo bar is particularly suitable for damaged and thin hair. Lavender also has a soothing effect on your scalp and is therefore good as an anti-dandruff shampoo. Fill your shower with a floral sea of ​​scents with this lavender shampoo bar!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Lavender shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Lavender is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Extract, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Limonene, Coumarin, CI 51319\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938715111751,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-lavender-60g-646074.jpg?v=1739897186"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-ginger-orange-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Ginger Orange 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Ginger Orange shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. This shampoo bar contains a combination of various natural products such as Almond Oil, Coconut Butter, Macadamia Nut Oil and Olive Oil. These oils care and nourish your hair for a beautiful natural shine. The delicious ginger and orange extracts have been added to stimulate your senses and give you a boost!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Ginger Orange shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Ginger Orange is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Zingiber Officinale Root Extract, Raphanus Sativus (Radish) Root Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Linalool, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, CI 15985\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938730512711,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-ginger-orange-60g-623179.jpg?v=1739897166"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-cornflower-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Cornflower 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Cornflower shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type - and especially for men due to the heavier \u0026amp; fresh scent. Linden blossom extract has been added to this shampoo bar, which has a soothing effect on your scalp. It also helps renew and hydrate damaged skin, which also strengthens your hair roots. The result? A full head of healthy hair!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Cornflower shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Cornflower is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tilia Cordata Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Limonene, Coumarin, Alpha Isomethyl Ionone, Benzyl Benzoate, Geraniol, CI 42090\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938736804167,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-cornflower-60g-835077.jpg?v=1739897179"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-coconut-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Coconut 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the coconut shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type. However, this shampoo bar is particularly suitable for dyed and treated hair. Coconut oil cleanses your hair thoroughly in a mild manner, so that your color is not carried away. This is in contrast to more intensive shampoos. Coconut oil is known for its nourishing effect and has the ability to penetrate into the hair fiber, so it does not weigh down your hair. In addition, the intense aromas of the Coconut Shampoo bar help relax your senses so that you can have a stress-free day!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Coconut shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Coconut is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Hexyl Cinnamal, Benzyl Benzoate, Hydroxycitronellal, Citronellol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938745291079,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-coconut-60g-770588.jpg?v=1739897172"},{"product_id":"clarification-moisturizing-powder-shampoo-40g","title":"Clarification Moisturizing Powder Shampoo 40g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo with organic rice and corn powder is an innovative washing powder for hair. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a classic shampoo. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits also sensitive scalps.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePowder Shampoo 100% natural origin ingredients provide hydration, volume and shine to the hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe plastic-free packaging made from recycled aluminum is compact and light, easy to transport. And of course n\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eo sulfates, no preservatives.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Pour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, apply to already wet hair. Repeat if necessary for longer hair. Do not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Citric acid, Sodium chloride, Oryza Sativa St arch \/ Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch*, Zea Mays starch \/ Zea Mays (Corn) Starch*, Maltodextrin, aqua\/water, Kaolin, Sodium cocoate, Glucose, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Sodium Cocoyl Alaninate, Sodium Hyaluronate. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11,12% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50964771209543,"sku":null,"price":18.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-moisturizing-powder-shampoo-40g-903958.jpg?v=1739897182"},{"product_id":"clarification-the-volume-powder-dry-shampoo-35g","title":"Clarification The Volume Powder Dry Shampoo 35g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Volume Powder is ideal for sensitive scalps looking for a fresh feeling and texture between two shampoos. 100% ingredients of natural origin with corn starch, white clay and oat flour.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Sprinkle a small amount of powder in the palm of the hand, then apply the  powder on the roots. Gently massage the scalp to distribute the powder evenly and help absorb the sebum. Brush the hair until the powder totally disappears.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDo not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes. Wash hands after use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eZea Mays (corn) starch, Kaolin, Avena Sativa (Oat) kernel flour \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e95% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50964926988615,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-the-volume-powder-dry-shampoo-35g-186172.jpg?v=1739897196"},{"product_id":"clarification-duo-set-of-cleansing-powders-body-and-hair","title":"Clarification Duo Set of Cleansing Powders - Body and Hair","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe set includes The Moisturizing Powder Shampoo (40g) and The Body Wash Powder (40g), both offer a unique care experience.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo\u003c\/strong\u003e with organic rice and corn powder is an innovative washing powder for hair. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a classic shampoo. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits also sensitive scalps.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePowder Shampoo 100% natural origin ingredients provide hydration, volume and shine to the hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder\u003c\/strong\u003e with organic oats and white clay is very innovative. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a traditional shower gel. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits sensitive skin.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIt is the natural cleansing treatment for the body that gently moisturizes and cleanses all skin types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003ePour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, apply to already wet hair. Repeat if necessary for longer hair. Do not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003ePour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, add some drops of water and rub hands together until it foams, then apply on wet skin. Repeat if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDo not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Citric acid, Sodium chloride, Oryza Sativa St arch \/ Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch*, Zea Mays starch \/ Zea Mays (Corn) Starch*, Maltodextrin, aqua\/water, Kaolin, Sodium cocoate, Glucose, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Sodium Cocoyl Alaninate, Sodium Hyaluronate. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11,12% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSodium Lauroyl Glutamate, Aqua \/ Water, Kaolin, Avena Sativa Kernel Flour \/ Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Flour*, Sodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Citric Acid, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Glucose, Sodium Hyaluronate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965083717959,"sku":null,"price":34.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-duo-set-of-cleansing-powders-body-and-hair-537546.webp?v=1739897187"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-volumizing-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Volumizing Seabuckthorn Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural shampoo enriched with sea buckthorn oil is natural and gentle, which gives hair fluffiness and shine. Sea buckthorn oil strengthens the hair, provides the necessary nutrients to the hair and scalp, and helps prevent split ends. Wheat protein strengthens hair, stimulates hair growth and increases hair fluffiness and elasticity. Essential oils contribute to the normal functioning of the sebum secretion of the scalp and give a feeling of freshness.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including oily hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eprovides natural volume\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith cleansing effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair fluffiness and shine\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and strengthens the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a citrus scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eseabuckthorn oil to nourish the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emade with natural cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e98,58% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Vegetable Oil, Panthenol, Cetyl Alcohol, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Ricinus Communis Seed (Castor) Oil, Glycerin, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glyceryl Stearate, Citric Acid, Tocopherol (E-vitamin), Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110474252615,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-shampoo-250ml-549035.png?v=1740891413"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-softening-honey-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Softening Honey Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural honey shampoo makes the hair soft and easy to comb, nourishing the hair from roots to ends. Organic honey extract makes the hair silky and protects from environmental effects. Organic barley extract stimulates hair growth and gives shine. Wheat protein strengthens the hair and increases elasticity. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003estrengthens hair from root to tip\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a softening and protective effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair softness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eimproves hair structure \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a honey-sweet smell\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emade with mild, plant-based cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith natural bee glue extract\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99,22% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Panthenol, Hordeum Vulgare (Barlay) Extract, Glyceryl Oleate, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110637044039,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-softening-honey-shampoo-250ml-212888.png?v=1740891413"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-caring-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Caring Shampoo with Plum Oil 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLUUV natural shampoo with plum oil is suitable for everyday use for all hair types. Cold-pressed plum kernel oil moisturizes both the scalp and hair and protects hair from heat treatment. Natural betaine and aloe keep hair moisturized. Natural gentle plum shampoo makes hair well combed, silky and elastic. Suitable for both coloured and natural hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair and curly hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith caring and softening effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and protects your hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eprotects hair from heat treatment\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emild, plant-based cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle enough for everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith organic plum oil for a silky finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99,18% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate (and) Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Cocamidoprpyl Betaine, Glycerin, Betaine, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Citric Acid, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110671745351,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-caring-shampoo-with-plum-oil-250ml-277927.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV natural kids shampoo  – where fun meets healthy hair! This shampoo takes your child’s hair care to new heights with its completely natural, tear-free formula. Designed for little adventurers, it leaves hair strong, shiny, and gently detangles even the most resistant knots. With ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, you can trust that LUUV kids shampoo is not only gentle on your little one’s hair but also on the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCarefully selected herbal detergents are perfect for your child’s delicate scalp, ensuring a nurturing and soothing wash. Shampoo is also infused with the goodness of moisturizing aloe and plant betaine – not only does it make their hair easy to comb, but it also strengthens it from root to tip, leaving it looking healthy, vibrant, and ready for any adventure that comes their way. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is naturally derived and allergen-free. LUUV natural kids shampoo is not only natural but also vegan, making it a choice you can feel great about. Experience hair that’s as soft as a mother’s caress and join the fun today!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTear-free formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,4%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate, Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Citric Acid, Glyceryl Oleate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115336728903,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml-163262.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"petit-joliehair-body-shampoo-200ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Hair \u0026 Body Shampoo 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Hair\u0026amp;Body Shampoo cleanses and cares for the skin and hair in a mild way. The special composition ensures supple skin and prevents dehydration. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for children with dry and sensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt doesn't sting the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLike all our products, the baby hair \u0026amp; body shampoo does not contain parabens, SLS, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes. The baby shampoo is made from 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe bottle is made from 100% recycled plastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile taking a shower or bath, add a small amount of shampoo to your hand or washcloth and lightly massage the skin and hair of your baby. Rinse well with water afterwards.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Coco-Glucoside, Decyl Glucoside, Xanthan Gum, Glyceryl Oleate, Parfum*, Dicaprylyl Ether, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133856514375,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-hair-body-shampoo-200ml-339984.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"magrada-hair-stimulating-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-250ml-copy","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Shampoo With Linden Flower Extract Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTake the summer with you – the linden flower shampoo with birch extract is a powerful Nordic elixir which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The sweet scent of the shampoo will take you back to warm summer memories in a blink, bringing a smile to your face even on a bitterly cold winter morning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe invigorating shampoo will make your hair less frizzy, nurturing and moisturising the structure of the hair and giving it a beautiful gloss and shine. The organic plant extracts support hair growth and improve the elasticity of the hair. The hair is soft, light, flowing after washing!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for daily use for the entire family, including for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic Nordic birch extract\u003c\/span\u003e stimulates circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters*, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Glycerin, Alcohol, Panthenol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: \u003cspan\u003e97,44%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335029915975,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-travel-size-100ml-976915.png?v=1743213040"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-travel-size-100ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour hair is ready for invigoration. Indulge it with spring-like freshness, gloss, and shine!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe juicy rhubarb-enriched shampoo is designed for intensive enlivening of dry and damaged hair. The extra moisturising aloe extract with Pro-Vitamin B5 restores, nurtures, and reinforces the damaged hair structure. The vitamin treatment that your hair needs.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Citric Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract*, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Parfum, Panthenol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,57%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulfate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e| alcohol-free |\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335103545671,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":tru