\u003eNordic linden flower extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters*, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Glycerin, Alcohol, Panthenol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: \u003cspan\u003e97,44%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335146078535,"sku":null,"price":22.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-refill-500ml-513082.png?v=1743213039"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-500ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour hair is ready for invigoration. Indulge it with spring-like freshness, gloss, and shine!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe juicy rhubarb-enriched shampoo is designed for intensive enlivening of dry and damaged hair. The extra moisturising aloe extract with Pro-Vitamin B5 restores, nurtures, and reinforces the damaged hair structure. The vitamin treatment that your hair needs.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Citric Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract*, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Parfum, Panthenol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,57%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulfate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e| alcohol-free |\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335168753991,"sku":null,"price":25.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-500ml-952084.png?v=1743213042"},{"product_id":"bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-50ml","title":"BEE IT Nourishing Shampoo 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing shampoo for damaged hair and scalp. It cleanses with care, maintaining the original structure of the hair with an energetic action. The soft creamy texture creates a light lather with extra ordinary effectiveness for soft and vital hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to wet scalp and hair, massaging gently. Rinse gently, inhaling and exhaling slowly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Xanthan gum, Glycerin, Disodium cocoamphodiacetate, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Citric acid, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Panthenol, Argania spinosa kernel oil, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Mel\/Honey*, Coumarin, Limonene, Dehydroacetic acid, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, CI 19140 [Yellow 5].\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138350772551,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml-159598.jpg?v=1739897346"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-50ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u0