ash rich in natural ingredients to to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAmused and clean, leaves hair velvety and luminous and skin soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassiu\u003cimg\u003em sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143676195143,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-for-kids-maya-50ml-4970425.png?v=1756222789"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-shampoo-mandarin-200ml","title":"HOIA Natural Mandarin Shampoo 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHOIA’s Natural Shampoo Mandarin is a gentle shampoo made with deeply hydrating aloe vera, wheat protein, locally sourced nettle extract, and argan oil. The addition of organic mandarin essential oil gives the shampoo a delightful holiday aroma while potentially improving scalp circulation and protecting hair from environmental damage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis shampoo nourishes and strengthens hair while helping to prevent hair loss.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA Natural Shampoo contains no petroleum byproducts, parabens, silicones, sulfates, microplastics, synthetic preservatives, or fragrances. Its ingredients are 99% natural, with 84% of them being organically sourced. It doesn’t dry out your scalp and is gentle on your hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply an appropriate amount to wet hair and scalp, wash, and rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Sodium C14-16 Olen Sulfonate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Disodium Laureth Sulfosuccinate, Lauryl Glucoside, *Glycerin, Betain, Olive Oil Glycereth- 8 Esters, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Chloride, *Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, *Citrus Nobilis Peel Oil, Sodium Levulinate ,*Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, *Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Gluconate, Lactic Acid, **Citral, **Linalool, **Limonene. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural components of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247139516743,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-mandarin-shampoo-200ml-1044810.jpg?v=1756718905"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/sampoonid.oembed?page=4","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}